<p><img TITLE="_ahb0167" HEIGHT="426" ALT="_ahb0167" SRC="http://www.gigiphoto.com/blog/2010/03/_ahb0167.jpg" WIDTH="639" /></P>
<p><span></SPAN>最後在旁邊寫上我的名字就大功告成!</P>
<p><img TITLE="_ahb0191" HEIGHT="426" ALT="_ahb0191" SRC="http://www.gigiphoto.com/blog/2010/03/_ahb0191.jpg" WIDTH="639" /></P>
